the white house is hoping a new 10day visa 
that wont require foreigners to reveal their aids status will end 
threats of a boycott of an upcoming international conference on the 
disease in san francisco 
but it was unclear whether the action will be enough to satisfy 
critics of us immigration restrictions 
i dont know whether theyll view this as sufficient said 
