<TEXT>
the man leading lithuanias peaceful drive to win 
its independence from the soviet union is a softspoken 
57yearold music professor 
lithuanian president vytautas landsbergis lacks the charisma of 
polands lech walesa or czechoslovakias vaclav havel his efforts 
