been tortured were true that he deplored the action and promised 
it would not happen again 
unfortunately it is true that some of these people who have 
complained were in fact tortured but once the anc became aware 
immediate steps were taken to discipline those who were quilty of 
torturing other people he said 
mandela did not specify the punishment inflicted on those 
responsible for the torture but he said the commanders of the 
camps where the torture took place had been dismissed 
